#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:3
msgid "Call layout"
msgstr "Leagan amach glaonna"

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:5
msgid ""
"You can switch between grid view and speaker view using the toggle icon in "
"the three-dot menu or the bottom bar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat aistriú idir radharc eangaí agus radharc an chainteora trí "
"úsáid a bhaint as an deilbhín scoránaigh sa roghchlár trí phointe nó sa "
"bharra bun."

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:11
msgid "Grid view"
msgstr "Radharc eangaí"

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:13
msgid ""
"Grid view shows all participants as tiles. Use the navigation buttons on the"
" left and right to scroll through participants when they do not all fit on "
"the screen."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an radharc eangaí na rannpháirtithe uile mar thíleanna. Úsáid na"
" cnaipí nascleanúna ar chlé agus ar dheis chun scrollú trí na rannpháirtithe"
" nuair nach n-oireann siad go léir ar an scáileán."

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:19
msgid "Speaker view"
msgstr "Radharc cainteora"

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:21
msgid ""
"Speaker view (also called promoted view) centres the active speaker in a "
"large tile and places the other participants in a row below. Use the "
"navigation buttons on the left and right to scroll through participants when"
" the row overflows."
msgstr ""
"Lárnaíonn radharc an chainteora (ar a dtugtar radharc cur chun cinn freisin)"
" an cainteoir gníomhach i dtíl mhór agus cuireann sé na rannpháirtithe eile "
"i sraith faoi. Bain úsáid as na cnaipí nascleanúna ar chlé agus ar dheis "
"chun scrollú trí na rannpháirtithe nuair a bhíonn an tsraith ró-líonta."
